{
  "title": "Bitter Gooey Venezuelan Peanut Casserole",
  "description": "A weeknight Venezuelan dish featuring peanut brittle, this casserole is a unique blend of bitter and gooey flavors. It's a vegan-friendly option that's perfect for a quick dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
